title: Norwegian Opens Sales Office in Australia
text:
Norwegian Opens Sales Office in Australia June 30, 2015 
Norwegian Cruise Line is opening a sales and marketing center in Sydney, Australia. In a statement, the company said its goal is to meet a growing demand for cruise travel in Australia, New Zealand and the Pacific. The office will represent three brands--Norwegian, Oceania Cruises and Regent Seven Seasâ€”and will offer on-site support for travel industry partners and representatives in Australia. 0
